flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Initialize<br/>cycle counter"]
    B --> C{More cycles?}
    C -->|No| Z([End])
    C -->|Yes| D["Poll email inbox"]
    D --> E{New emails?}
    E -->|No| F["Sleep until<br/>next interval"]
    F --> G["Increment cycle"]
    G --> C
    E -->|Yes| H["LLM: Summarize<br/>message"]
    H --> I["LLM: Suggest<br/>reply action"]
    I --> J["Log summary<br/>and action"]
    J --> F